# 8. 君はヒーロー

Children: Nyantaro! Thanks for getting the Ferris wheel to work again!
Tsukasa: Hah hah hah! Seeing all of you enjoy the carnival puts a big smile on my face!
Children: Oh, Nyantaro, can we take a picture with you?!
Tsukasa: Yes, of course! I'll even strike one of my cool cat poses for all of you.
Children: A cool pose...?! I wanna do it too!
Tsukasa: Yes, you're welcome to join me. Raise one leg, and do this...!
Nene: They really love Tsukasa now.
Airi: I mean, he did just save the carnival. It only seems natural they'd want to talk to him.
Children: Oh, it's the cat sisters!
Children: You two were so cute during the show! Can we shake hands?
Children: Yeah, I wanna shake hands with you both too.
Airi: Yes, of course...! Why don't you all form a line for us here?
Mother: Excuse me... You two were also a part of the show, yes?
Minori: Huh? Us?
Mother: Yes, my little one apparently wants to thank the both of you...
Children: H-Hi...! I was able to cheer for Nyantaro because you two encouraged me to, so...
Children: Thanks for cheering together with me...!
Minori & Mizuki: You're very welcome!
Tsukasa: Alright, I hope you all keep enjoying your visit!
Children: We will! Thanks, Nyantaro!
Children: Bye bye!
Tsukasa: (Thank goodness they're all smiling again...)
???: <Nice work, Tsukasa☆>
Miku: <Your show ended up being a super huge success!>
Tsukasa: Ah, Miku, perfect timing! I was just thinking I needed to thank you.
Tsukasa: That show wouldn't have gone as well as it did without your assistance...
Tsukasa: So, thank you very much. You really saved the day!
Miku: <Hehe! I'm just glad that everyone's smiling from ear to ear☆>
Airi's Voice: Oh, Tenma, there you are!
Tsukasa: Oh, Airi Momoi, all of you! And...
Inuyama: Wonderful work, Tenma.
Tsukasa: Mr. Inuyama! I didn't realize you were with them.
Inuyama: Yes, I wanted to thank you all properly.
Inuyama: That really was a wonderful spectacle. From the bottom of my heart, thank you...
Tsukasa: Mr. Inuyama...
Inuyama: Despite what happened, you all managed to put on a show which mirrored the one we put on when this carnival first opened. No, this was even more fantastic.
Inuyama: From everybody watching the show to those having fun at the other attractions, this place began overflowing with smiles and laughter.
Inuyama: I can say with certainty that I'm never going to forget this day.
Inuyama: Thank you all for saving my carnival. I couldn't have asked for better heroes!
Airi: Hehe. It feels a little strange being told that after playing a villain during the show... But I'm really glad to hear it!
Tsukasa: Yes. However, if heroes are people who strive to make others smile...
Tsukasa: Then I believe all the joy you've brought with this carnival makes you a hero as well, Mr. Inuyama!
Inuyama: Tenma...
Nyantaro: Meow!
Minori: Hi, Nyantaro!
Mizuki: You disappeared before the show started... Where were you all this time?
Inuyama: Ah, he was actually right near the Ferris wheel the entire time.
Inuyama: He seemed worried about it being stopped... But now that he knows it's back up and running, I think he decided to go for a walk around the carnival.
Tsukasa: I see. In other words, you kept watch as we did our show. Right under our noses, no less...
Tsukasa: Ever since I met you, each day has felt like a whirlwind for some reason...
Tsukasa: It all began at that pond... Then, you became my running partner, and even introduced us to this incredible carnival!
Tsukasa: I'm beyond glad that we met, Nyantaro, and I enjoyed every minute of the time we spent together!
Nyantaro: Meow!
Inuyama: I also need to thank you, Nyantaro...
Inuyama: Yes, Tenma and the others here kept everyone smiling by putting on their show...
Inuyama: But I was able to meet them because of you.
Tsukasa: I see... In other words, you were responsible for making sure Mr. Inuyama kept smiling.
Tsukasa: Which means...
Tsukasa: You're a hero too, Nyantaro... Both to this carnival, and to Mr. Inuyama!
Nyantaro: Meow!
Inuyama: Alright, there's still some time left before the carnival is scheduled to close. I hope you have as much fun as you can until then, everyone.
Nyantaro: Meow.
Minori: Oh, Nyantaro's started walking...!
Nene: Does this mean he's gonna show us around again...?
Airi: Then, let's follow him like we did last time, shall we?
Mizuki: Yeah! Let's keep making fun memories together until the very end!
Tsukasa: Alright, then...
Tsukasa: Where to first, Nyantaro?!
Nyantaro: Meow!
